    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and primarily garage-kept, offering a fantastic balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor rock chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side bumper consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the premium leather seats are supple, showing only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. I have followed a strict maintenance schedule, recently replacing the brake pads and performing a full synthetic oil change. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and confident ride. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a comprehensive folder of service records. This is a dependable, well-presented vehicle that is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
